name: pitbull guardian angel necklace
description:
I printed my pitbull guardian angel onto plastic and baked it. The sides are gold leafed and the front is coated for protection with a high gloss finish. Although the finishing process helps protect this pendant, it should not be worn while swimming or bathing.

	Please be aware that due to the handmade nature of these pendants, that your design placement may vary slightly…..but will still look fabulous! Each pendant comes with its own oxidized metal chain.

	Shipped within 5 days.
